HEADWORD: Ratiocinate
<hw>Ra`ti*oc"i*nate</hw>
<pr>(r⟦acr⟧sh`⟦icr⟧*⟦ocr⟧s"⟦icr⟧*n⟦amac⟧t)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos>
